title: Watcha Got? - Rob Tunbridge
description:
Rob Tunbridge is an unsigned singer/songwriter based in Chelmsford, 

Essex England.

You can find out more at: my space or search for Rob Tunbridge on you 

tube




This ZIP file contains the full album + Original Artwork in PDF Format


Tracks are MP3@192K and have been tested in i-tunes, windows media 

player, VLC Player


Tracks are:

 1. Oh! Amanda
 2. Watcha Got?
 3. Freedom
 4. I'm Going Home
 5. Nothing U Can Do
 6. Fine, Fine, Fine!
 7. No Time For Delay
 8. Play With Fire
 9. Doesn't Matter
10. Over & Done
11. The Apartment Song
12. Diamond Night


NOTE
tracks 10 & 11 should play as one complete track but most players add 

a 2 second gap between tracks. If possible remove this gap before 

playing back.



Hope you like them!
